---
import Foundation from '../../../assets/placeholder_about/Foundation.png';
import growthExpansion from '../../../assets/placeholder_about/growth-expansion.jpg';
import innovation from '../../../assets/placeholder_about/innovation.jpg';
---

<section class="relative py-28 px-4 overflow-hidden bg-background">

	<div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
		<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[450px] h-[450px] bg-accent/10 blur-[140px] rounded-full"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[450px] h-[450px] bg-accent/10 blur-[140px] rounded-full"></div>
	</div>

	<div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

		<div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24">
			<p class="text-accent tracking-[0.3em] font-semibold mb-4">
				OUR JOURNEY
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
				The Story Behind
				<span class="text-accent"> Avietho</span>
			</h2>

			<p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-8">
				Since 2018, Avietho Digital Marketing has grown from a passionate
				creative team into a trusted digital marketing partner for businesses,
				government agencies, and political leaders across the Philippines.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="relative">

			<div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-accent/30 -translate-x-1/2"></div>

			<div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-24">

	<div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
	<div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-accent/20 bg-card h-[320px]">
		<img
			src={Foundation.src}
			alt="Foundation"
			class="w-full h-full object-cover"
			loading="lazy"
		/>
	</div>
</div>

				<div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative">

	<span class="text-accent font-semibold tracking-wider">
		2018
	</span>

					<h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mt-3 mb-5">
						Foundation
					</h3>

					<p class="text-text-subtle leading-8">
						Avietho Digital Marketing was established in Muntinlupa City with
						a vision of helping businesses build stronger digital identities
						through creativity, strategy, and innovation. From the very
						beginning, the company focused on delivering measurable results
						and long-term partnerships.
					</p>

				</div>

			</div>

<div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-24">

	<div>

		<span class="text-accent font-semibold tracking-wider">
			2020
		</span>

		<h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mt-3 mb-5">
			Growth & Expansion
		</h3>

		<p class="text-text-subtle leading-8">
			As demand increased, Avietho expanded its expertise into political
			campaigns, multimedia production, branding, government projects,
			and integrated digital marketing solutions, becoming a full-service
			creative agency.
		</p>

	</div>

	<div>
		<div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-accent/20 bg-card h-[320px]">
			<img
				src={growthExpansion.src}
				alt="Growth & Expansion"
				class="w-full h-full object-cover"
				loading="lazy"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>

</div>

<div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

	<div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
		<div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-accent/20 bg-card h-[320px]">
			<img
				src={innovation.src}
				alt="Innovation"
				class="w-full h-full object-cover"
				loading="lazy"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative">

		<span class="text-accent font-semibold tracking-wider">
			2023
		</span>

		<h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mt-3 mb-5">
			Innovation
		</h3>

		<p class="text-text-subtle leading-8">
			Today, Avietho continues to innovate through web development,
			multimedia production, branding, digital campaigns, and
			data-driven marketing strategies that help organizations thrive
			in an ever-changing digital landscape.
		</p>

	</div>

</div>

	</div>

</div>

</section>